<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>OTP Verification</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f0f4f8; padding: 40px 16px; margin: 0; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #4f46e5);
      border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
      padding: 32px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
    .logo span { font-weight: 400; opacity: 0.85; }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 44px 40px;
      border-left: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-right: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .greeting { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a202c; margin: 0 0 12px 0; }
    .greeting span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .subtext { font-size: 15px; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 32px 0; }

    .label {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    }
    .otp-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f7ff, #eef2ff);
      border: 2px dashed #c7d2fe;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .otp-code { font-size: 44px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 12px; color: #4f46e5; margin: 0; }
    .otp-expiry { margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8; }

    .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 28px 0; }

    .warning {
      background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fde68a;
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px;
      font-size: 13px; color: #92400e; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .support { font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
    .support a { color: #4f46e5; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }

    .footer {
      background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-text { font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; }
    .footer-text a { color: #64748b; }
    .footer-brand { font-size: 12px; color: #cbd5e1; margin: 6px 0 0 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">

  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">PH <span>Healthcare</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <p class="greeting">Hello, <span><%= name %> &#128075;</span></p>
    <p class="subtext">
      We received a request to verify your identity. Use the one-time password
      below to complete the process. This code is valid for <strong>2 minutes</strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="label">Your one-time password</p>
    <div class="otp-box">
      <p class="otp-code"><%= otp %></p>
      <p class="otp-expiry">&#9203; Expires in 2 minutes</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider"/>

    <div class="warning">
      &#9888;&#65039; <strong>Never share this code with anyone.</strong>
      Our team will never ask for your OTP. If you did not request this,
      please ignore this email or contact support immediately.
    </div>

    <p class="support">
      Need help? Reach out to us at
      <a href="mailto:support@phhealthcare.com">support@phhealthcare.com</a>
      and we will get back to you as soon as possible.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p class="footer-text">
      You are receiving this because a sign-in was attempted for your account.<br/>
      <a href="#">Unsubscribe</a> &middot;
      <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> &middot;
      <a href="#">Terms of Service</a>
    </p>
    <p class="footer-brand">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> PH Healthcare. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>